<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - ABC Retail</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@600&display=swap"> <!-- Link to Google Font -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@700&display=swap"> <!-- New font for buttons -->
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #FFDAB9; /* Light background color for body */
            color: #333; /* Darker text color */
            overflow-x: hidden; /* Prevent horizontal scroll */
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #343a40; /* Dark grey background for the navbar */
            padding: 1px 20px;
            display: flex; /* Use flexbox for alignment */
            justify-content: center; /* Center content horizontally */
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #f8f9fa; /* Light text color for the navbar */
            text-align: center; /* Center align text */
        }

        .hero {
            background: url('https://t4.ftcdn.net/jpg/06/34/09/69/360_F_634096945_nT013AXOaokOmXXU0mRlfSLmnSbbmZXw.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
            color: #f8f9fa; /* Light text color for hero section */
            min-height: 100vh; /* Cover entire viewport height */
            padding: 120px 20px; /* Increased padding for better spacing */
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: none; /* Remove any border around the hero section */
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4rem; /* Increased font size for better visibility */
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #f8f9fa; /* Light text color for better visibility */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); /* Add shadow for better readability */
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.75rem; /* Increased font size for better readability */
            line-height: 1.4; /* Improve line spacing */
            font-weight: 300; /* Light font weight for a modern look */
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); /* Add shadow for better readability */
            color: #8b6d5c; /* Light text color */
            max-width: 800px; /* Limit the width for better readability */
            margin: 0 auto; /* Center the paragraph */
        }

        .btn-primary {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; /* Apply new font */
            background: #FA8072; /* Gradient background */
            border: none;
            padding: 15px; /* Adjust padding for consistent button size */
            font-size: 1.25rem; /* Larger font size for the buttons */
            border-radius: 30px;
            transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
            margin: 15px; /* Increased margin between buttons */
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); /* Add shadow for better effect */

            color: #ffffff; /* White text color for better contrast */
            width: 200px; /* Fixed width for all buttons */
            height: 60px; /* Fixed height for all buttons */
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold; /* Bold text for better visibility */
        }

            .btn-primary:hover {
                background: #FFC0CB; /* Darker gradient on hover */
                transform: scale(1.05);
                box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); /* Enhanced shadow on hover */
            }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); /* 2 columns */
            gap: 30px; /* Increased space between buttons */
            max-width: 800px; /* Limit the width for better alignment */
            margin: 0 auto; /* Center the grid */
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 10px 20px; /* Reduced padding for a compact footer */
            background-color: transparent; /* Remove background color */
            color: #6c757d; /* Light text color */
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            border-top: none; /* Remove top border if any */
        }

            .footer p {
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                font-size: 0.875rem; /* Smaller font size */
            }

            .footer .social-icons {
                margin-top: 10px;
            }

                .footer .social-icons a {
                    color: #f8f9fa; /* Light text color for social icons */
                    margin: 0 10px;
                    font-size: 1.5rem;
                    text-decoration: none;
                }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Welcome to ABC Retail</h1>
            <p>ABC Retail: Revolutionizing online retail with scalable cloud solutions to handle peak shopping seasons, streamline order processing, and enhance customer experiences with real-time analytics and reliable messaging.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <a href="@Url.Action("Index","Customer")" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Customers</a>
                <a href="@Url.Action("Index","Product")" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Products</a>
                <a href="@Url.Action("Index","Order")" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Orders</a>
                <a href="@Url.Action("Index","Files")" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Files</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p></p>
        <div class="social-icons">
            <a href="#"><i class="bi bi-facebook"></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i class="bi bi-twitter"></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i></a>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.3.0/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>